                "invention-title": [
                    "Reducing gas flow adjusting method for hydrogen-based reduction shaft furnace",
                    "一种氢基还原竖炉还原气流调节方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a hydrogen-based reduction shaft furnace reducing gas flow adjusting method which comprises the steps that large-diameter pellet furnace charge is arranged in a furnace to form a high-porosity furnace charge area, small-diameter pellet furnace charge is arranged in the furnace to form a low-porosity furnace charge area, the volume of the high-porosity furnace charge area accounts for 12-30% of the volume of the whole furnace charge, and the volume of the low-porosity furnace charge area accounts for 12-30% of the volume of the whole furnace charge; and the whole furnace burden is equal to the sum of the large-diameter pellet furnace burden and the small-diameter pellet furnace burden. The central temperature and the reduction efficiency of the shaft furnace can be effectively improved, and the production efficiency of sponge iron is greatly improved; the gas flow speed of a side road is inhibited, the residence time of the reducing gas in the shaft furnace can be effectively prolonged, the hydrogen component has more time to be in contact with the iron-containing furnace charge, the high consumption intensity of the reducing gas allows the proportion of hydrogen in the reaction gas proportion to be greatly increased, clean energy is effectively used in smelting, carbon emission can be reduced, and the energy consumption is reduced. The goal of carbon neutralization is achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "发明公开了一种氢基还原竖炉还原气流调节方法，在炉内布置大直径球团矿炉料形成高孔隙率炉料区域，在炉内布置小直径球团矿炉料形成低孔隙率炉料区域，且高孔隙率炉料区域体积占整体炉料体积的12～30％，整体炉料等于大直径球团矿炉料与小直径球团矿炉料之和。可以有效的提高竖炉中心温度和还原效率，大幅增加海绵铁的生产效率；抑制边路气流速度，可以有效的延长还原性气体在竖炉内的停留时间，使得氢气成分有更多的时间与含铁炉料进行接触，还原性气体的高消耗强度允许反应气体配比中氢气的占比大幅提升，清洁能源在冶炼中的有效使用，可以减少碳排放，达成碳中和的目标。"
                }
            ]
